name: the feelgood space goat of IO
description: Deep in the cosmos, noshing on stardust & space debris resides a goat of Io, His mission in this exquisite existence is to roam the universe to rise the vibe & upgrade your frequency. You'll need to do your work but he gives you the drive to thrive. So if you find the Goat of IO, take a moment & breathe, drift deep within, & listen. He will be speaking to your heart, you'll know when his words have landed. goat also says you get a free tee of the same design with purchase
